      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Feathered Frenzy",
        "Client": "Buddy Handler Iori",
        "Description": "I\u0027m sorry Hunter... Those Buddies\r\nheard that there were \u0022ghosts\u0022 at\r\nthe Shrine Ruins and ran off. I\u0027m\r\nso worried about them with that\r\nAknosom around. Can you hunt\r\nit while I go look for them!?",
        "Target": "Hunt an Aknosom",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Fr\u00E9n\u00E9sie \u00E0 plumes",
        "Client": "Iori l\u0027assistant Pilpoil",
        "Description": "\u00C7a m\u0027emb\u00EAte, mais... ces\r\n\u0022fant\u00F4mes\u0022 au Temple oubli\u00E9\r\nont fait fuir ces Pilpoils.\r\nJe m\u0027inqui\u00E8te pour eux avec\r\ncet Aknosom dans les parages.\r\nTu pourrais t\u0027occuper de lui\r\npendant que je les cherche ?",
        "Target": "Chasser un Aknosom",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Frenesia piumata",
        "Client": "Iori l\u0027assis. dei compagni",
        "Description": "Purtroppo, quei compagni hanno\r\nsentito che c\u0027erano dei\r\n\u0022fantasmi\u0022 alle Rovine sacre e\r\nsono corsi l\u00E0. Sono\r\npreoccupato per loro, con\r\nquell\u0027Aknosom in giro. Gli dai\r\nla caccia mentre io li cerco?",
        "Target": "Caccia un Aknosom",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Federrausch",
        "Client": "Buddy-Wildexperte Iori",
        "Description": "Entschuldige... Zwei Buddys\r\nhaben von \u0022Geistern\u0022 bei den\r\nHeiligen Ruinen geh\u00F6rt und\r\nsind weggerannt. Ich mache mir\r\nSorgen wegen dem Aknosom dort.\r\nKannst du ihn jagen, w\u00E4hrend\r\nich die Buddys suche?!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Aknosom.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Frenes\u00ED emplumado",
        "Client": "Iori el gestor de camaradas",
        "Description": "Algunos camaradas huyeron al\r\no\u00EDr lo del fantasma del Templo\r\nolvidado. Me preocupa que les\r\npueda pasar algo con ese\r\nAknosom suelto... \u00BFTe puedes\r\nencargar de \u00E9l mientras yo\r\nbusco a los camaradas?",
        "Target": "Caza un Aknosom",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u041F\u0435\u0440\u043D\u0430\u0442\u0430\u044F \u044F\u0440\u043E\u0441\u0442\u044C",
